      "raw_text": "WASHINGTON, May Sowing to\na shortage of coal in the far east,\ndue to the war, President Hill of the\nGreat Northern has requested the\nnavy departments permission to pur-\nchase from the American naval sup\nply in the orient enough to supply the\nsteamship Minnesota on her return\ntrip to the Pacific coast. 1t is said\nhis request will be granted."
